                </FooterDetails>
                <Header/>
                <Paragraph>The Peace Corps posts certain types of records that it creates on its website. A formal FOIA request is not necessary to access them. The Peace Corps also maintains a FOIA requester service center that can provide information on the status of a person's FOIA request.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
